title: Bondi Boys MC
notes: The Bondi Boys Motor Club (BBMC) or Bondi Boys & Babes Motor Club is a criminal gang operating out of Vespucci, founded by Irwin Dundee.

title: LSM
notes: The Little Seoul Mafia (LSM) is a big family of criminals that have each other backs. If you mess with one of us you mess with all of us. This organization was founded by Dan J with Josh Powell’s help.

title: Mine
notes: Go down to the mines to farm some gems to sell to Jewelled Dragon or get metal parts to sell to Mechanic Shops!

title: Sanitation
notes: Go here to exchange your hard-earned materials!

title: Alta Street Apartments
notes: The Apartments is where new players wake up.

title: Golf Course
notes: Fancy a game of golf? Head up there and try out /golf.

title: Mega Mall
notes: A place to buy repair kits, radios, and body armor.

title: Sandy Shores PD
notes: The Sandy Shores Sheriff's Office, along  Los Santos Police Department, the San Andreas State Police and the San Andreas State Park Rangers, makes up the executive branch of Los Santos; together they ensure that the law is upheld and enforced.

title: Impound Lot
notes: Where cars go when they get impounded.

title: Mission Row PD
notes: The Los Santos Police Department, along  Sandy Shores Sheriff's Office, the San Andreas State Police and the San Andreas State Park Rangers, makes up the executive branch of Los Santos; together they ensure that the law is upheld and enforced.

title: The Courthouse
notes: Where all legal proceedings such as courtcases are taken place.

title: Bolingbroke Penitentiary
notes: It is governed by the San Andreas State Prison Authority. The prison is located on the Los Santos County side of Route 68, just down the road from Harmony. The prison's shape is that of an octagon. The perimeter of the prison is patrolled by the Los Santos County Sheriff and the Los Santos Police Department. There are armed San Andreas State Prison Authority officers standing near the entrances, making sure that no one attempts to break in or out.

title: El Burro Heights Fire Station
notes: El Burro Heights Fire Station is an official office of EMS.
